en_321009_0	A basic Tamil Language Course, aimed at enhancing Tamil proficiency among military personnel of the 66 Infantry Division under the guidance of Brigadier Mangala Wijesundara, General Officer Commanding, 66 Infantry Division came to a draw on Wednesday (2).
en_321009_1	The 14-day-long course was followed by 21 students at the Battalion Training School under the supervision of Lieutenant Colonel Prashantha Ekanayaka, Chief Instructor.
en_321009_2	This will help students to maintain civil-military relations in a better manner.
